      "name": "Balance",
      "effect": "Your starting hand will reflect the card balance of your Deck. This Skill will not activate unless you have at least 6 of each type of card (Monster, Spell, and Trap) in your Deck.\nYou cannot Special Summon or activate monster effects until the end of the Main Phase of your first turn."
    },
